Neto: &quot;It's an important result for the team. The team keeps progressing. I want to congratulate everyone for our performance, even while being a man down for the large part of the match.&quot; <br />
<br />
&quot;Keeping a clean sheet fills you with confidence going forward, anyone that knows anything about football knows that. I'm happy for the result and for my team-mates. The important thing is getting results. That's the key thing.&quot;
